name: Parallel Woof
description:
A Shiba is trying to find his way home, but along the way he realizes that he can shift dimensions. He uses those abilities to solve problems that he comes across while trying to escape the forest.

Winnitron compatible controls:

Move left/right:                      Left/right arrow key

Jump:                                           Up arrow key

Bark/Shift dimensions:      "." key
